%p 
	Searching for an apartment in NYC is painful. We hope the agent provides you with positive guidance. In the meantime, feel free to continue browsing 
	%a{href: 'https://www.transparentcity.co/?utm_source=email&utm_medium=sender', target: '_blank'} Transparentcity. 
	Best of luck on your hunt!

%table
	%tr
		%td To:
		%td=@to_email
	%tr
		%td Phone #:
		%td=@phone
	%tr
		%td Interested In:
		%td=@neighborhoods.present? ? @neighborhoods.join(', ') : ''
	%tr
		%td Bedrooms
		%td=@bedrooms
	%tr
		%td Budget:
		%td=@budget

%p=simple_format(@message)


:css
	*{
		font-family: 'Open Sans', sans-serif !important;
	}

	table tr td, p, a{
		font-size: 14px;
	}

	table tr td{
		border: none;
	}